  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::MapDialogue
  dialogueLines:
  - "-Anh em sinh \u0111\xF4i-C\xE1c ng\u01B0\u1EDDi l\xE0 ai, sao c\xF3 th\u1EC3
    v\u01B0\u1EE3t qua b\u1ECDn qu\xE1i v\u1EADt ph\xEDa sau v\u1EADy?"
  - "-B\u1EA1n-Ta l\xE0 ho\xE0ng t\u1EED c\u1EE7a v\u01B0\u01A1ng qu\u1ED1c, \u0111i
    c\xF9ng c\xE1c chi\u1EBFn binh c\u1EE7a ta gi\u1EA3i c\u1EE9u qu\u1ED1c \u0111\xF4"
  - "-Anh em sinh \u0111\xF4i-R\u1EA5t h\xE2n h\u1EA1nh g\u1EB7p ng\xE0i, ch\xFAng
    t\xF4i th\u1EA5y nhi\u1EC1u qu\xE1i v\u1EADt xu\u1EA5t hi\u1EC7n n\xEAn \u0111\xE3
    l\u1EBBn qua ch\xFAng \u0111\u1EBFn \u0111\xE2y, kh\xF4ng ng\u1EDD v\xF9ng \u0111\u1EA5t
    ph\xEDa tr\u01B0\u1EDBc \u0111\xE3 b\u1ECB \u0103n m\xF2n b\u1EDFi n\u0103ng
    l\u1EF1c h\u1EAFc \xE1m"
  - "-B\u1EA1n-Ch\u1EC9 c\xF3 v\u01B0\u1EE3t qua \u0111\xE1m qu\xE1i v\u1EADt ch\xFAng
    ta m\u1EDBi c\xF3 th\u1EC3 ti\u1EBFn g\u1EA7n h\u01A1n s\u1EF1 th\u1EADt, c\xE1c
    anh s\u1EBD \u0111i c\xF9ng t\xF4i ch\u1EE9?"
  - "-Anh em sinh \u0111\xF4i-OK GOAT"
